'''Rich Hedden''' wrote "[[Three Against the Galaxy]]," a comic featured in [[Star Wars Tales 3|''Star Wars Tales'' #3]]. He also provided artwork for [[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine|''Star Wars Galaxy'' magazine]] of a [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorrean]] [[Gamorrean guard|guard]], possibly of his own creation, [[Grissom (Gamorrean)|Grissom]].

